I was confused...

32
00:03:23,740 --> 00:03:24,839
还有点醉
... drunk.

33
00:03:26,341 --> 00:03:27,840
我觉得
I think...

34
00:03:27,841 --> 00:03:30,140
我只是想吓一吓他们
... mostly I wanted to scare them.

35
00:03:30,141 --> 00:03:33,541
