Yes, sir. Absolutely, sir.

90
00:07:18,563 --> 00:07:20,562
我是说，我得到了教训
I mean, I learned my lesson.

91
00:07:21,664 --> 00:07:25,064
我敢说我已经完全改变了
I can honestly say that I'm a changed man.

92
00:07:28,364 --> 00:07:30,863
