I admit I didn't think much of Andy first time I laid eyes on him.

136
00:12:03,490 --> 00:12:06,389
他看起来似乎风一吹就会倒
Looked like a stiff breeze would blow him over.

137
00:12:06,790 --> 00:12:09,089
