Put your trust in the Lord.

169
00:14:06,601 --> 00:14:08,800
你们的身体交给我
Your ass belongs to me.

170
00:14:10,702 --> 00:14:12,601
欢迎来到肖申克监狱
Welcome to Shawshank.

171
00:14:17,703 --> 00:14:19,102
解开他们
Unhook them.

172
00:14:24,503 --> 00:14:25,902
