You underestimate yourself.

1396
01:44:41,090 --> 01:44:42,683
我不这样看
I don't think so.

1397
01:44:46,530 --> 01:44:50,465
在此我能供应物品给你，但是……
In here I'm the guy who can get things for you, sure, but...

1398
01:44:51,235 --> 01:44:53,759
